name: TEMPORARY SUSPENSION OF DROPS ON HICETNUNC
description: Dear Collectors and Other artists, there's a serious exploit happening in HicEtNunc at the moment, where a scammer can mint works under another wallet address. The artwork will show as a genuine real piece, with the current wallet address BUT IT IS A FAKE. We're waiting for a fix. So for now do not buy anything from my account, and check @Ruben_Fro on twitter for updates (not here). Thank you
